data.description: Welcome to your new home in the coveted community of Lake Park, Award winning schools, and an array of amenities. Move in ready, nestled in the sought- after Lake Park Subdivision, and Swim/Tennis community. This charming property has a cozy front porch, and when you walk in you discover an open flow between kitchen and the living room. Very spacious home with a completed bonus room seen in pictures, which is not added in the square footage. The Large backyard enclosed by a privacy fence, provides ample space for gatherings, activities, and enjoyment. Hvac is only one year old, and Dishwasher was replaced 2 years ago. Conveniently located new historic downtown Acworth, shopping centers, and parks. This home is an ideal blend of comfort, and convenience. This property is just not a house; its a place to call home.
